.SH NAME
isatty \- show whether default streams are terminals
.SH SYNOPSIS
.BR "isatty"
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B isatty
is a simple program which shows whether the default streams (stdin,
stdout, stderr) are connected to a terminal. 

.SH SEE ALSO
.BR modglue (1).
.BR ptywrap (1).

